content.comment:
Dear reviewers,

In order to make this work more complete and convincing, we have revised our paper on the following parts:
(1) add the recent state-of-the-art baselines;
(2) implement our algorithm on ``Feature Generating Networks for Zero-Shot Learning’’ to prove the generalization ability of domain division;
(3) fix some typos and errors;
(4) clarify some confusing parts.

Note: The complex part of our paper includes the definitions and derivations based on the extreme value theory. Our goal is to make the paper logical, amenable, and reasonable, so it cannot be very easy to illustrate the core mathematical concept in a short page.

We would be very appreciated if you can take a closer look.

Thank you!

